text: Sinzing is a municipality in Regensburg in Bavaria in Germany. ==Geography== Sinzing is on the Schwarzen Laber and the Danube, about eight kilometers west of Regensburg. ==Municipality structure== There are 17 districts Adlstein Alling Bergmatting Bruckdorf Dürnstetten Eilsbrunn Grafenried Hart (PLZ 93152) Kleinprüfening Kohlstadt Kühblöß Mariaort Minoritenhof Niederviehhausen Oberalling Reichenstetten Riegling Saxberg Schneckenbach Sinzing Steg Thalhof Unteralling Viehhausen Vogelsang Waltenhofen Zeiler (PLZ 93152) ==References== Category:Regensburg (district)
